com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.errors

Class WZSDKError

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.errors.WZError
      • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.errors.WZSDKError

  • public class WZSDKError
extends WZError
    The error code identifiers for errors generated by the core API classes. Errors are normally reported as part of the WZStatus object returned by many of the API methods.
